The definitive story of the England v West Germany 
semi-final from Italia 90 - a match that captivated the 
nation and restored pride in the beautiful game. 20 years

also includes rarely-seen archive footage from the 1990 
World Cup. Featuring Paul Gascoigne, Terry Butcher, 
David Platt, Peter Shilton, Mark Wright, Des Lynam,
